high_descs: Turn right and head straight, then hang left towards the sofa.
Pick up tomato from the sofa.
Go straight towards the wall and then walk straight into the room, turning to the microwave on your right.
Place tomato on the microwave.
After turning around and going straight, proceed to turn to the left towards the sofa.
Pick up tomato from the sofa.
Go straight towards the wall and then walk straight into the room, turning to the microwave on your right.
Place tomato on the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Collecting tomato from different places and arranging them on a microwave to heat it.

high_descs: Arriving at the table, turn right. After the table, turn left. In the middle of the table, turn right, approach the sofa.
Take the tomato on the right.
Turn right. At the end of the table, turn right. Go to the middle of the table, near the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the tomato. Close the microwave.
Turn around. Turn left Reach the middle of the sofa, turn right.
Take the tomato.
Turn right. After the table, turn right. Reach the middle of the table, near the microwave.
Open the microwave. Place the tomato inside the microwave to the right of the other. Close the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Find two tomatoes and place them inside the microwave.

high_descs: Walk straight and turn right to reach the sofa
Take a tomato from the sofa
Turn back and walk towards the microwave oven
Open the oven and put the tomato inside and close the oven
Turn back and walk towards the sofa again
Take one more tomato from the sofa
Turn back and walk towards the microwave oven
Open the oven and put the tomato along with the first tomato and close the oven
anns.task_desc: Put the tomato in the oven
